description: MITRE Pre ATK informational drawbacks within the OSRS CMCF are related to instances where information from an artifiact is found missing, irrelevant, not congruent, or not complete based on the information supplied within the artifact.  The informational drawbacks allow for the tracking of these types of informational defficiencies.
name: OSRS MITRE Pre ATK Informational Drawbacks

values.description: The artifact contains MITRE Pre ATK related to Priority Definition Planning information that is uncertain, indefinite, or unclear of character or meaning.
